      "content": "wait what do you mean a goblin can steal a pie? i was just asking about the chemistry. can you just stick to the science of the metabolic pathway? specifically how the lactate threshold works and what exactly is happening at the cellular level with the hydrogen ions?",
      "source": "evaluator"
